{"tid":1551840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】疑法庭「擺烏龍」 黃之鋒機場過關被捕","createTime":"2019-09-08T07:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T08:05:31.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"186376d7ac4ed175ac52ffe09f099457d3d0fe26","tid":1551840,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190908/large/1567927585_3fcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190908%2Flarge%2F1567927585_3fcd.jpg&h=df79de82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒今日準備前往外地參與演講，接近下午2時許於機場過關時被O記探員拘捕，消息指他違反保釋條件。據悉黃之鋒被捕屬誤會，因為法庭「擺烏龍」誤將周庭出發前往外地的日期，錯寫成黃之鋒出發的日期，導致他「違反保釋條件」。早前黃之鋒亦已於本月3日到訪台灣出席研討會及與立法委員會面。<br />\n<br />\n早前警方就6.21示威者包圍警總以涉嫌「煽惑他人參與未經批准的集結」、「組織未經批准的集結」及「明知而參與未經批准的集結」拘捕黃之鋒，同時亦以涉嫌「煽惑他人參與未經批准的集結」及「明知而參與未經批准的集結」拘捕周庭。兩人於東區法院提堂，獲准以保一萬元現金保釋，每星期兩次向警署報到，須遵守宵禁令（晚上11時至翌日早上7時），兩人也不准踏入警察總部一帶範圍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，法庭亦允許兩人前往外地出席早已安排的演講、會議等，包括黃之鋒早前已安排前往德國就「柏林圍牆倒下」發表演講，以及到紐約接受時代周刊訪問及與國會議員見面，並會於9月23日返港。而周庭亦已安排在9月中旬到德國出席研討會，以及到奧地利探親。<br />\n<br />\n案件押後十星期至11月8日下午再訊，以待警方作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190908/60022773?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F60022773%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=acfb4d7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190908%2F60022773%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6d400efb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190908/60022773?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"a3243b024eaf2158862a641af1315a11c5077172","tid":1551840,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de9d197df81b5e4d26eb6b52adea46e13d6fe64","tid":1551840,"uid":229459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"法庭有無咁on9<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d90dfe7c0a50bd070d06e8b4cc2357c0cf0a7ca","tid":1551840,"uid":34010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"乜鳩文件都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8532997a94924bd97836eca4a7df523b75def04e","tid":1551840,"uid":36065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"擺明故意"},{"pid":"0c105098914e3f4e4241a6ced47a1d69084ed2f7","tid":1551840,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bb1f9f1ff3cf134be4f7c7b8f6117282e5cd31","tid":1551840,"uid":201427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"咩擺烏龍茶擺明搵藉口搞鳩佢啦"},{"pid":"8137a5a0b0fb403c480329d6debbe469c73f1832","tid":1551840,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"樣樣都錯講法治"},{"pid":"3f82444ce45da6ddd929ff593cfee65132629042","tid":1551840,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ae4f989b6074798e1b37c886f5c1aeed9ef4ac","tid":1551840,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:05:31.000Z","msg":"想做佢又怕美國報復縮沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}